《'''公报'''》（{{lang-en|The Gazette}}），中文全称《'''宾夕法尼亚公报'''》<ref>{{cite book|author1=杰伊·布莱克编著|author2=詹宁斯·布莱恩特编著|author3=苏珊·汤普森编著|coauthors=张咏华编著|title=大众传播通论|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=aPRBDwAAQBAJ&pg=PT206|date=2017-12-07|publisher=飞翔时代|pages=206–|id=GGKEY:3JB0W5B0EYB|access-date=2020-07-04|archive-date=2020-07-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200715204507/https://books.google.com/books?id=aPRBDwAAQBAJ&pg=PT206|dead-url=no}}</ref>（{{lang|en|The Pennsylvania Gazette}}）<ref name="WendlerTremml2013">{{cite book|author1=Michael Wendler|author2=Bernd Tremml|author3=Bernard John Buecker|title=Key Aspects of German Business Law: A Practical Manual|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=Nj6bBwAAQBAJ&pg=PA211|date=2013-06-05|publisher=Springer Science & Business Media|isbn=978-3-540-24776-0|pages=211–|access-date=2020-07-04|archive-date=2020-08-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200802030705/https://books.google.com/books?id=Nj6bBwAAQBAJ&pg=PA211|dead-url=no}}</ref>，简称《'''宾州公报'''》<ref name="何日生2017">{{cite book|author=何日生|title=建构式新闻|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=fjFsDwAAQBAJ&pg=PA330|date=2017-09-13|publisher=五南图书出版股份有限公司|isbn=978-957-11-9311-3|pages=330–|access-date=2020-07-04|archive-date=2020-08-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200802042926/https://books.google.com/books?id=fjFsDwAAQBAJ&pg=PA330|dead-url=no}}</ref>（Pennsylvania Gazette）<ref name="Shen1966">{{cite book|author=Zonglin Shen|title=Pao hspueh|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=GNgVAAAAMAAJ|year=1966|pages=114–|access-date=2020-07-04|archive-date=2020-08-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200802035242/https://books.google.com/books?id=GNgVAAAAMAAJ|dead-url=no}}</ref>，是[[美国|美国]]最著名的[[报纸|报纸]]之一，存在于1728年[[美国独立战争|美国独立战争]]之前到1800年。该报由[[塞缪尔·凯默|塞缪尔·凯默]]（Samuel Keimer<ref name="contributors">{{cite book|author=Wikipedia contributors|title=Focus On: 100 Most Popular American Autobiographers|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=Os5CDwAAQBAJ&pg=RA3-PA1936|publisher=e-artnow sro|pages=3–|id=GGKEY:BRS6TPYR76F|access-date=2020-07-04|archive-date=2020-07-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200715204705/https://books.google.com/books?id=Os5CDwAAQBAJ&pg=RA3-PA1936|dead-url=no}}</ref>）于1728年12月24日首次出版<ref name="on1940">{{cite book|author=Best Books on|title=Pennsylvania; a Guide to the Keystone State,|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=OkPJS1Z8kA0C&pg=PA133|year=1940|publisher=Best Books on|isbn=978-1-62376-037-3|pages=133–|access-date=2020-07-04|archive-date=2020-08-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200802043039/https://books.google.com/books?id=OkPJS1Z8kA0C&pg=PA133|dead-url=no}}</ref>，是[[宾夕法尼亚州|宾夕法尼亚州]]出版的第二份报纸，时名《对所有艺术和科学的普遍教导及宾夕法尼亚公报》（The Universal Instructor in all Arts and Sciences: and Pennsylvania Gazette<ref name="Mease1811">{{cite book|author=James Mease|title=The Picture of Philadelphia: Giving an Account of Its Origin, Increase and Improvements in Arts, Sciences, Manufactures, Commerce and Revenue|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=nDYVAAAAYAAJ&pg=PA82|year=1811|publisher=B. & T. Kite, no. 20, N. Third-street. For Sale by them and Joseph Delaplaine.|pages=82–|access-date=2020-07-04|archive-date=2020-07-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200706035708/https://books.google.com/books?id=nDYVAAAAYAAJ&pg=PA82|dead-url=no}}</ref>），暗指凯默意图在他的报纸上印制[[伊弗雷姆·钱伯斯|伊弗雷姆·钱伯斯]]（Ephraim Chambers）的《[[百科全书；或艺术与科学通用字典|百科全书]]》（Cyclopædia, or an Universal Dictionary of Arts and Sciences）<ref name="loc">{{cite web|title=Pennsylvania Gazette, Philadelphia|url=https://www.loc.gov/rr/news/circulars/pagazette.txt|accessdate=2006-12-07|date=2006|publisher=Library of Congress|archive-date=2017-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170211072600/http://www.loc.gov/rr/news/circulars/pagazette.txt|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

1729年10月2日，[[本杰明·富兰克林|本杰明·富兰克林]]（Benjamin Franklin）和[[休·梅雷迪斯|休·梅雷迪斯]]（Hugh Meredith）买下了这份报纸，并将其名字简化为《宾夕法尼亚公报》<ref name="蔡骐蔡雯1998">{{cite book|author1=蔡骐|author2=蔡雯|title=美国传媒与大众文化: 200年美国传播现象透视|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=19YpAQAAIAAJ|year=1998|publisher=新华出版社|isbn=978-7-5011-4074-9|pages=43–|access-date=2020-07-04|archive-date=2020-08-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200802043017/https://books.google.com/books?id=19YpAQAAIAAJ|dead-url=no}}</ref>，同时也放弃了凯默试图印制钱伯斯的《[[百科全书；或艺术与科学通用字典|百科全书]]》的宏伟计划<ref name="loc" />。富兰克林不仅印刷了这份报纸，还经经常用[[化名|化名]]向报纸投稿。他的报纸很快成为[[殖民地|殖民地]]最成功的报纸。

